FBIS3-52506 "drnes003_r_94002" FBIS-NES-94-003 Document Type:Daily Report 5 Jan 1994 India BJP Urges Government Report on Kashmir Talks BK0401125694 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1230 GMT 4 Jan 94 BK0401125694 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The BJP [Bharatiya Janata Party] says the government should take political parties into confidence and apprise them of the details of the foreign secretary-level talks held between India and Pakistan. Talking to newsmen in New Delhi today, the party spokesman, Mr. K.L. Sharma, also wanted the government to spell out its future course of action as Islamabad seems to have taken an unreasonable attitude at the talks.
